6. Packet switching vs circuit switching - when is each better?
7. What is encapsulation?

## Key Formulas

- Transmission delay = L/R
- Propagation delay = d/s
- Traffic intensity = La/R
- Total nodal delay = d_proc + d_queue + d_trans + d_prop